snippet.title: The King of Cats // Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2265680/The_King_of_Cats/

Navigate the claustrophobic corridors of a cargo ship and try to survive a night with man-eating tigers on the loose. Your choices will determine who lives and who dies.

Developed by Witching Metal Prod.
